<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <title>Account Recovery</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333;">
  <div style="max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px;">
    <h2 style="color: #1a73e8;">Account Recovery Request</h2>
    <p>Dear <%= firstName %>,</p>
    <p>We received a request to recover your account details for 247 Active Trading. Below are your account details:</p>
    
    <table style="width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; margin: 20px 0;">
      <tr style="background-color: #f5f5f5;">
        <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Email</td>
        <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><%= email %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Password</td>
        <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><%= password %></td>
      </tr>
      <tr style="background-color: #f5f5f5;">
        <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">2FA Secret</td>
        <td style="padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd;"><%= twoFASecret %></td>
      </tr>
    </table>
    
    <p><strong>Recovery Requested:</strong> <%= recoveryDate %></p>
    <p><strong>Important:</strong> For security reasons, please change your password immediately after logging in and update your 2FA settings if needed.</p>
    <p>If you did not request this recovery, please contact our support team immediately at support@247activetrading.com.</p>
    
    <p>Best regards,<br>The 247 Active Trading Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>